Pincus, Appellant, v. Dry Dock, E. B. & B. R. Co., Respondent. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. March 31, 1892.) Action by Isaac Pincus against the Dry Dock, East Broadway & Battery Railroad Co.

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and O’Brien and Ingraham, JJ.

No opinion. Motion to dismiss appeal granted, with $10 costs.
